This policy governs how we conduct usage of your data.

When we say "Azumi Development", "we", "us", and "our", we mean Azumi Development and its related entities.

When we say "services", we mean our services, website, and other products.

When we say "you" or "your", we mean you. If accessing our services on behalf of a legal entity, you agree that you have the authority to bind that entity to these terms, and “you” and “your” will refer to that entity.



Your data is supplied to us automatically as soon as you agree to these terms.



Your data is used to:

- Survey usage of our services.
- Improve our services.
- Provide to you our best customized experience for you.
- Provide these services to you.
  - Without your data, we cannot process any requests for our service.

- Your data may be used with or without warning.
  - However, any data provided is anonymous. We value your privacy.







We will never ever sell or source your data or private information.






If you do not agree to this policy, we cannot provide you our services.


PRIVACY POLICY IS SUBJECT TO CHANGE
